name: Warmup_Div01_Sub03
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD1S3.CPF,
GmailD1S3.NOME,
GmailD1S3.EMAIL,
GmailD1S3.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S3.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD1S3.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD1S3.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD1S3.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV01_SUB03 GmailD1S3
UNION
